Mr. Jayabarathan Chelliah, M.A. (U.S.A), B.Ed.<br>

Mr. Jayabarathan Chelliah, the founder and Correspondent of the school, is the Managing Trustee of the Mount Zion Christian Education Trust. He holds a bachelor’s degree in science from Alagappa University, Karaikudi, Tamil Nadu, a bachelor's degree in education from Calicut University, Kerala. He graduated in June, 1978 with a master’s degree in Educational administration from the prestigious Loma Linda University, California, U.S.A.

He is also the founder and Chairman of Mount Zion College of Engineering and Technology at Pudukkottai, Tamil Nadu and Mount Zion College of Nursing, Pudukkottai, Tamil Nadu.

He along with his team of trustees who are dedicated, qualified educationists, has been governing these three institutions with foresight and meticulous planning. He has over 40 years of experience in managing various educational institutions. The relentless perseverance of the trustees for academic excellence ensures that students get the best of all aspects of education.
